### Feedback Report API Tests (Updated - All Users Can Report)

### 1. Report Feedback as Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Feedback/report
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ratingId": 1,
    "reason": "Feedback này chứa nội dung không phù hợp"
}

### 2. Report Feedback as Tour Guide
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Feedback/report
Authorization: Bearer {{tourGuideToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ratingId": 1,
    "reason": "Feedback này có thông tin sai lệch"
}

### 3. Report Feedback as Tour Operator (existing functionality)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Feedback/report
Authorization: Bearer {{tourOperatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ratingId": 1,
    "reason": "Feedback này không chính xác về dịch vụ của chúng tôi"
}

### 4. Report Feedback as Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Feedback/report
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ratingId": 1,
    "reason": "Feedback này vi phạm quy tắc cộng đồng"
}

### 5. Try to report non-existent feedback
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Feedback/report
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ratingId": 999,
    "reason": "Test non-existent feedback"
}

### 6. Try to report without authentication
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Feedback/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ratingId": 1,
    "reason": "Test without auth"
}

### Variables (set these in your environment)
# @baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
# @customerToken = your_customer_jwt_token_here
# @tourGuideToken = your_tour_guide_jwt_token_here
# @tourOperatorToken = your_tour_operator_jwt_token_here
# @adminToken = your_admin_jwt_token_here 